mmendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"推荐服务响应时间异常激增：正常平均耗时约4-12秒，异常时段激增至54-58秒，延迟倍数高达442-440倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误(549次)和context canceled错误(504次)，表明推荐服务异常导致前端服务级联故障\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端调用推荐服务的ListRecommendations接口出现严重超时和连接错误，包括i/o timeout和transport is closing错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析\n\n### 1. 主要异常模式\n- **推荐服务(recommendationservice)是根因**：该服务响应时间从正常的4-12秒激增至54-58秒，延迟倍数高达440倍以上\n- **前端服务是主要受害者**：由于推荐服务异常，前端服务出现大量500错误和context canceled错误\n\n### 2. 错误传播路径\n```\nFrontend (入口) → RecommendationService (根因)\n  ├── 前端出现HTTP 500错误\n  ├── 推荐服务调用超时(timeout)\n  └── 连接超时(i/o timeout)和传输关闭(transport closing)\n```\n\n### 3. 故障特征\n- **延迟类型**：严重响应时间延迟(rrt_max)\n- **错误类型**：连接超时、传输错误、上下文取消\n- **影响范围**：所有前端实例(frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2)都受到影响\n\n### 4. 根因定位\n根据调用链分析，推荐服务是最下游的异常服务，其异常直接导致前端服务的级联故障。推荐服务本身可能由于资源不足、数据库连接问题或内部处理逻辑异常导致了严重的性能下降。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "e4ef8a12-193", "component": "recommendationservice", "reason": "rrt_max spike from 4-12s to 54-58s causing severe performance degradation and cascading failures", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(recommendationservice)", "observation": "rrt_max increased from 4-12s to 54-58s, 440x performance degradation"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(frontend)", "observation": "context can